{"title":"Blog 主题更改","uid":"1828396dcb62aff8de00fb0b79b85c29","slug":"Blog-主题更改","date":"2025-03-12T06:22:33.000Z","updated":"2025-03-12T14:32:30.444Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Blog-主题更改.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/Blog_theme_change.jpg","content":"<p>今天正式更改了一下Blog的主题，主要体现在颜色搭配上。原先的主题颜色太妖艳，现在更改成比较成熟稳重的配色,更符合我的审美。</p>\n<p>配色的思路来源于日落后的20分钟————“蓝调时刻”，但夕阳的美丽是不可能用几种简单的配色来组成的。</p>\n<p>经过几次试验，最终选定这种颜色搭配：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">color_1: &#x27;#E19112&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">color_2: &#x27;#4B0082&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">color_3: &#x27;#0052d4&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>更改前的主题界面：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/140532.png\" alt=\"picture\"></p>\n<p>更改后的主题界面：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/140511.png\" alt=\"picture\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>Today, I officially changed my blog’s theme, mainly in terms of color coordination. The previous theme was too gaudy, and now I’ve switched to a more mature and steady color scheme that better suits my aesthetic.</p>\n<p>The color - matching idea comes from the 20 minutes after sunset - the “blue hour”. But the beauty of the sunset can’t be simply made up of a few colors.</p>\n<p>After several trials, I finally chose this color combination:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">color_1: &#x27;#E19112&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">color_2: &#x27;#4B0082&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">color_3: &#x27;#0052d4&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>The blog theme before the change:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/140532.png\" alt=\"picture\"></p>\n<p>The blog theme after the change:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/140511.png\" alt=\"picture\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"今天正式更改了一下Blog的主题，主要体现在颜色搭配上。原先的主题颜色太妖艳，现在更改成比较成熟稳重的配色,更符合我的审美。 配色的思路来源于日落后的20分钟—...","permalink":"/post/Blog-主题更改","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":832,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"2025-03","slug":"2025-03","count":6,"path":"api/categories/2025-03.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Study","slug":"Study","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Study.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Aurorp1g","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"一枚热爱计算机的博主","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Aurorp1g","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"HTML学习总结","uid":"c701bbe2a68c2c09453c83556e12c209","slug":"HTML学习总结","date":"2025-03-11T07:05:30.000Z","updated":"2025-03-12T14:33:05.527Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HTML学习总结.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/HTML.png","text":"写个笔记对HTML语法进行简单总结 HTML简介HTML（HyperText Markup Language）即超文本标记语言，是用于创建网页的标准标记语言。它...","permalink":"/post/HTML学习总结","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.1k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"2025-03","slug":"2025-03","count":6,"path":"api/categories/2025-03.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":1,"path":"api/tags/HTML.json"},{"name":"Study","slug":"Study","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Study.json"}],"author":{"name":"Aurorp1g","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"一枚热爱计算机的博主","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Aurorp1g","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true}}